title: Hulk/Spider-Man Toilet Paper - The Gamma Gambit (1979) (DCP-HD)
description:
Contains:     325 sheets of 2-ply facial-quality tissue

                 ... no, wait ...

              Hulk and Spider-Man Toilet Paper - The Gamma Gambit (1979) (ToyJesus-
                                                                          DCP-HD)



Quality:      This is one of those gorgeous high-resolution scans ToyJesus are known
              for. Unfortunately, the original was printed on, you guessed it,
              toilet paper, so the resultant quality is still pretty crappy.

              Whoops, bad choice of words there on my part. The quality stinks?
              Uh... the quality is fairly low. Hah, there you go, that'll do.



Disclaimer:   In case anyone decides to try and print this out on actual toilet
              paper in turn, this uploader cannot be held responsible for any
              resultant damage suffered by your printer.

              I'd advise to use the blank kind, though, not something that already
              has a pattern, the strip is hard enough to read as it is.

              And do tell us about the experience in the comments. Photographic
              proof absolutely not, repeat, NOT, required!
